{"tid":2478516,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"研究發現武肺患者縱康復 1/3人卻現精神問題","createTime":"2021-04-07T06:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T06:25:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac905d98ea6369c9ca4bcd6b8da9ef147cdbcec","tid":2478516,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:20:51.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐全球多時，即使確診者經已康復，卻繼續深受其後遺症影響。有研究發現，美國逾23萬名武肺患者在康復後六個月，有三分一患者出現精神或腦部上的問題。但研究人員強調，暫未確認武漢肺炎與精神問題之間存在關聯。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210407/3XGIOZ234ZCNZBLZWJBQN45RHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210407%2F3XGIOZ234ZCNZBLZWJBQN45RHI%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtD44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=ed472e09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210407%2F3XGIOZ234ZCNZBLZWJBQN45RHI%2F&h=58101c38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210407/3XGIOZ234ZCNZBLZWJBQN45RHI/</a>"},{"pid":"01958f5a99bdccc30bcadfb9b0bcd909f7f0c77b","tid":2478516,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"研究只信英國"},{"pid":"92a7aefa52f56e1e1a2798220bc62c2baf4f8448","tid":2478516,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"有冇 healthy control 同期做比較先<br />\n<br />\n可能疫情加經濟問題等等，overall 都多左人情緒問題呢"},{"pid":"70a69b87c11598e9107ce753459f1f29e30a8bca","tid":2478516,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92a7aefa52f56e1e1a2798220bc62c2baf4f8448","tid":2478516,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"有冇 healthy control 同期做比較先<br />\n<br />\n可能疫情加經濟問題等等，overall 都多左人情緒問題呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"／研究人員又把武肺患者數據，跟逾10萬名流感患者和23.6萬名呼吸道患者作比對。結果發現，武肺患者出現精神問題的風險，較流感患者高出44%，較其他呼吸道患者則高出16%。／<br />\n<br />\n風險過左44%，唔係整體精神病比率增44%"},{"pid":"01